Use the standard library
This is how to largest_smallest_integers of lst:
   Remember that positives is []
   Remember that negatives is []
   Remember that i is 0

   Do this lst's length times:
      Remember that x is item i in lst
      When x is more than 0, then:
         Add positives to x
      But, if not:
         When x is less than 0, then:
            Add negatives to x
         End when
      End when
      Increase i
   End do

   Remember that largest_negative is []
   Remember that smallest_positive is []

   When negatives' length is more than 0, then:
      Remember that largest_negative is max of negatives
   End when

   When positives' length is more than 0, then:
      Remember that smallest_positive is min of positives
   End when

   The answer is [largest_negative, smallest_positive]
